Assent	#488.	 say yes to, say ditto, amen to, say aye to. acknowledge, own, admit, allow, avow, confess
Disclosure	#529.	 split. acknowledge, allow, concede, grant, admit, own, own up to, confess, avow, throw off all disguise, turn inside out, make a clean breast
Affirmation	#535.	 advance, allege, propose, propound, enunciate, broach, set forth, hold out, maintain, contend, pronounce, pretend. depose, depone, aver, avow, avouch, asseverate, swear
